com.vmware.nsx.loadbalancer

Class LoadbalancerFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.loadbalancer.LoadbalancerFactory

  • public class LoadbalancerFactory
extends Object
    LoadbalancerFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx.loadbalancer package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
